Package: googleAuthR
Type: Package
Version: 1.4.0
Title: Authenticate and Create Google APIs
Description: Create R functions that interact with OAuth2 Google APIs 
    <https://developers.google.com/apis-explorer/> easily,
    with auto-refresh and Shiny compatibility.
